      "text": "Summer used to go, it was a place where it was a manufacturer of bricks, used to make bricks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, and over there was a huge lake.",
